</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0807D756FFBCFFB9FF09FB75FCB932D3" blockId="8.[175,1006,422,1247]" pageId="8" pageNumber="421">
<emphasis id="3ACC0B44FFBCFFB9FF09FB75FEB432C8" bold="true" box="[199,371,1199,1220]" pageId="8" pageNumber="421">Natural History.</emphasis>
There is no information available on the natural history of this species. Adults have been collected in mid-elevation moist tropical forest.
</paragraph>
